@startuml
autonumber

Actor User
Participant "Frontend (React)" as Frontend
Participant "Web API (Controllers)" as API
Participant "Business Logic (Services)" as BusinessLogic
Database "PostgreSQL" as Database

User -> Frontend: Uploads Excel file for ingestion
Frontend -> API: POST /transactions/upload/excel (Excel File)

alt Successful Upload and Processing
    API -> BusinessLogic: Call ingestExcel service (Excel File)
    BusinessLogic -> BusinessLogic: Parse Excel, extract transaction data
    BusinessLogic -> BusinessLogic: Attempt automatic category resolution (e.g., based on rules, past transactions)
    BusinessLogic -> Database: Database for each info needs (e.g category resolve)
    Database -> BusinessLogic: Gets the info
    BusinessLogic -> Database: Batch insert/update transactions (with resolved/suggested categories)
    Database --> BusinessLogic: Success / Inserted/Updated transaction IDs
    BusinessLogic --> API: Summary of ingested transactions
    API --> Frontend: Summary / Transactions requiring manual review
    Frontend --> User: Displays ingestion summary
else Upload or Processing Failed
    API --> Frontend: Error message (e.g., Invalid file format, Processing error)
    Frontend --> User: Displays Error message
end

@enduml